  83:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      *** LTDC HAL driver macros list ***
  84:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      =============================================
  85:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      [..]
  86:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****        Below the list of most used macros in LTDC HAL driver.
  87:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
  88:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_ENABLE: Enable the LTDC.
  89:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_DISABLE: Disable the LTDC.
  90:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_LAYER_ENABLE: Enable an LTDC Layer.
  91:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_LAYER_DISABLE: Disable an LTDC Layer.
  92:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_RELOAD_IMMEDIATE_CONFIG: Reload  Layer Configuration.
  93:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_GET_FLAG: Get the LTDC pending flags.
  94:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_CLEAR_FLAG: Clear the LTDC pending flags.
  95:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_ENABLE_IT: Enable the specified LTDC interrupts.
  96:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_DISABLE_IT: Disable the specified LTDC interrupts.
  97:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) __HAL_LTDC_GET_IT_SOURCE: Check whether the specified LTDC interrupt has occurred or not.
  98:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
  99:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      [..]
