 101:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 102:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 103:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      *** Callback registration ***
 104:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      =============================================
 105:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      [..]
 106:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      The compilation define  USE_HAL_LTDC_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
 107:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
 108:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      Use function HAL_LTDC_RegisterCallback() to register a callback.
 109:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 110:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 111:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Function HAL_LTDC_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
 112:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) LineEventCallback   : LTDC Line Event Callback.
 113:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ReloadEventCallback : LTDC Reload Event Callback.
 114:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ErrorCallback       : LTDC Error Callback
 115:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspInitCallback     : LTDC MspInit.
 116:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspDeInitCallback   : LTDC MspDeInit.
 117:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 118:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the callback ID
 119:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     and a pointer to the user callback function.
 120:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 121:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 122:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Use function HAL_LTDC_UnRegisterCallback() to reset a callback to the default
 123:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     weak function.
 124:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     HAL_LTDC_UnRegisterCallback() takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle
 125:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     and the callback ID.
 126:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 127:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     This function allows to reset following callbacks:
 128:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) LineEventCallback   : LTDC Line Event Callback
 129:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ReloadEventCallback : LTDC Reload Event Callback
 130:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ErrorCallback       : LTDC Error Callback
 131:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspInitCallback     : LTDC MspInit
 132:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspDeInitCallback   : LTDC MspDeInit.
