3579:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * @brief Set the configuration for a specific layer of the LTDC controller.
3580:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *
3581:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * This function configures a layer of the LTDC controller with the specified parameters.
3582:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * It sets the pixel format stride, window positioning, color frame buffer address, auxiliary
3583:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * frame buffer addresses, buffer length, and line number based on the layer configuration.
3584:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * It also handles the mirroring configuration for the layer if specified.
3585:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *
3586:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * @param hltdc Pointer to a LTDC_HandleTypeDef structure that contains
3587:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *              the configuration information for the specified LTDC.
3588:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * @param Aux0Addr Auxiliary frame buffer address 0 used for certain pixel formats.
3589:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * @param Aux1Addr Auxiliary frame buffer address 1 used for certain pixel formats.
3590:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   * @param Mirror Specifies the mirroring configuration for the layer. This parameter
3591:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *               can be one of the following values:
3592:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *               @arg LTDC_MIRROR_NONE: No mirroring.
