3602:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *       defines the number of bytes per pixel and hence the stride (the increment from one
3603:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   *       pixel to the next in a row of pixels). The function configures the layer window size
